T1  - Efficient Estimation of Arc Criticalities in Stochastic Activity Networks
AU  - Bowman, R. A.
Y1  - 1995/01/01
PY  - 1995
DA  - 1995/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.41.1.58
