TY  - JOUR
T1  - Forecaster Diversity and the Benefits of Combining Forecasts
AU  - Batchelor, Roy
AU  - Dua, Pami
Y1  - 1995/01/01
PY  - 1995
DA  - 1995/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.41.1.68
